Documented_Experience:
Experiences with using the tool are included in a webinar organised by the IUCN WCPA Transboundary Conservation Specialist Group with the following presentations:
An overview of the Diagnostic tool for transboundary conservation planners by Maja Vasilijević;
Experience with implementing the diagnostic tool in Europe by Boris Erg, The use of the tool to develop a Joint Management Plan for the Lower Awash Lake Abbe Transboundary Conservation Landscape between Djibouti and Ethiopia by Dominique Verdugo;
Using the tool as part of an educational process with students in the transboundary context by Todd Walters
